WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 8=

01:50.660 --> 01:52.820
(Chong Camp)

01:52.940 --> 01:53.780
Get out of the way!

02:03.270 --> 02:04.550
Are you faking all this

02:04.550 --> 02:05.420
or did you lose the bet?

02:07.470 --> 02:08.620
It's not over yet.

02:10.180 --> 02:11.460
It's too early to call it.

02:13.110 --> 02:13.950
Your Grace,

02:14.790 --> 02:16.350
were you satisfied with the first half?

02:19.300 --> 02:21.390
To sell the act,
you got yourself into danger.

02:22.070 --> 02:23.620
This is truly unexpected.

02:24.860 --> 02:26.620
Since when did you suspect him?

02:27.270 --> 02:28.110
From the very start,

02:28.580 --> 02:29.550
I smelled it in him,

02:29.550 --> 02:30.580
the scent of my own kind.

02:30.900 --> 02:31.900
Of your kind?

02:34.350 --> 02:36.020
Then he's definitely no good.

02:37.620 --> 02:38.460
Of course.

02:39.390 --> 02:40.230
Only members

02:41.460 --> 02:42.700
of the Chong royal family

02:43.420 --> 02:44.260
or the All-Knowing

02:45.550 --> 02:46.390
know about this duel.

02:47.740 --> 02:48.580
All-Knowing?

02:49.180 --> 02:50.070
A secret organization

02:50.070 --> 02:50.910
under the royal clan.

02:52.110 --> 02:53.790
It trains loyal assassins.

02:54.790 --> 02:55.630
The Blindfolded Trial

02:55.830 --> 02:57.140
is the graduation rite

02:57.620 --> 02:58.620
for all the disciples.

03:00.580 --> 03:01.990
Royal family members

03:02.580 --> 03:04.270
watch the blindfolded duels.

03:05.140 --> 03:05.980
The winner

03:06.350 --> 03:07.420
gets a name and graduates.

03:10.020 --> 03:11.790
Fifteen is the code name
of the fake Lin Jun.

03:13.860 --> 03:15.180
Disciples from different batches

03:15.620 --> 03:16.460
never meet.

03:17.140 --> 03:18.180
Han Lingqiu was disfigured.

03:19.550 --> 03:20.790
So Fifteen didn't recognize him.

03:24.620 --> 03:25.670
Then, Your Grace,

03:26.790 --> 03:28.350
since when did you notice Lin Jun?

03:29.830 --> 03:30.830
At first sight.

03:31.740 --> 03:33.830
Anyone who always wears
a human skin mask

03:34.620 --> 03:35.950
is no good anyway.

03:41.230 --> 03:42.550
This place is heavily guarded.

03:43.300 --> 03:44.420
You can't escape.

03:47.230 --> 03:48.300
Will you make a wish

03:48.550 --> 03:49.670
and let me grant it?

03:51.990 --> 03:53.350
Your Grace, are you not

03:54.110 --> 03:55.580
taking advantage of my plight?

03:56.580 --> 03:57.460
I don't think so.

03:59.510 --> 04:00.350
Believe it or not,

04:01.390 --> 04:02.390
even though I'm here,

04:03.180 --> 04:04.700
I can still break free on my own.

04:07.180 --> 04:08.420
The best part is yet to come.

04:09.950 --> 04:11.230
Be patient and wait.

04:16.860 --> 04:20.260
(Liang)

04:20.260 --> 04:21.100
Wait.

04:23.110 --> 04:24.630
What's wrong? Shouldn't we go?

04:33.470 --> 04:34.350
Are you saying

04:35.110 --> 04:36.350
these are the General's orders?

04:36.740 --> 04:37.670
Exactly.

04:37.670 --> 04:38.860
These are his plans.

05:09.990 --> 05:11.030
Who on earth are you?

05:16.550 --> 05:18.260
A little torture like this

05:19.260 --> 05:20.470
won't get a single word

05:20.470 --> 05:21.380
out of your prisoner.

05:22.940 --> 05:25.150
Are you so immersed
in your role as Lin Jun

05:26.260 --> 05:27.500
that you'd forget your training

05:27.500 --> 05:28.380
at the All-Knowing?

05:29.790 --> 05:30.790
Master Fifteen.

05:33.710 --> 05:35.180
How can you be sure that I'm Fifteen?

05:37.710 --> 05:38.670
Judging by age,

05:38.670 --> 05:40.470
you're Fifteen, Sixteen, or Seventeen.

05:41.380 --> 05:42.790
Sixteen was crippled in an accident.

05:43.620 --> 05:45.030
Seventeen has been missing for ages.

05:47.300 --> 05:48.790
So, you must be Fifteen.

05:56.550 --> 05:57.910
Who are you really?

06:00.550 --> 06:02.150
Who do you think

06:02.820 --> 06:03.910
was present at the Trial?

06:07.790 --> 06:08.790
You probably sneaked

06:10.150 --> 06:11.230
into Shuozhou to investigate

06:11.230 --> 06:12.470
the red bird thing.

06:13.300 --> 06:15.110
The High Priest
is particularly sensitive

06:15.590 --> 06:17.150
to any insult to Aphorisms of Cangshen.

06:20.030 --> 06:21.670
You can't figure out who I am

06:22.910 --> 06:24.820
and you've sensed
Han Lingqiu isn't ordinary.

06:25.060 --> 06:26.590
So you have to stay in Shuozhou

06:27.060 --> 06:28.860
and pass information to Awo'erqi too.

06:29.710 --> 06:30.670
Now, you've captured me,

06:30.670 --> 06:32.060
the commander of Shuozhou.

06:32.790 --> 06:34.820
If his rival Fenglai knows about it,

06:35.710 --> 06:36.670
what will he think?

06:43.180 --> 06:44.380
There's no need to show off

06:45.150 --> 06:46.670
how much you know about North Chong.

06:47.740 --> 06:49.110
Once you're brought to the court,

06:49.550 --> 06:51.300
everything shall be revealed.

06:53.790 --> 06:54.820
How did it feel

06:56.910 --> 06:57.750
to be "Mr. Lin"?

07:02.940 --> 07:04.150
You've spent your entire life

07:04.150 --> 07:05.790
playing all kinds of roles.

07:06.790 --> 07:08.420
I doubt you've ever lived

07:08.420 --> 07:09.820
as a warm and honest man, have you?

07:10.820 --> 07:11.820
Mr. Fifteen,

07:12.940 --> 07:14.470
when you watched Lin Huaide

07:14.910 --> 07:16.500
meet his end beneath the city walls,

07:16.820 --> 07:18.260
did you waver even for a moment?

07:19.110 --> 07:20.300
You deceived so many people.

07:22.790 --> 07:23.940
Was there ever a moment

07:25.910 --> 07:27.150
when you even deceived yourself?

07:32.060 --> 07:32.900
Get more guards here.

07:33.110 --> 07:34.060
Watch him closely.

07:34.060 --> 07:34.900
Yes.

07:39.380 --> 07:40.230
So long as he lives,

07:40.240 --> 07:41.670
he can't use his own name.

07:44.620 --> 07:46.230
What difference does it make if he dies?

07:47.620 --> 07:48.740
Am I right,

07:50.060 --> 07:50.910
Your Grace?

07:51.860 --> 07:53.030
If you keep thinking of him,

07:53.620 --> 07:55.230
you may die too.

07:57.910 --> 07:58.820
General Duan,

07:59.820 --> 08:01.350
you're in the enemy camp.

08:02.670 --> 08:03.620
They will take you

08:03.620 --> 08:04.860
to North Chong.

08:05.670 --> 08:06.530
Right now, Shuozhou

08:06.530 --> 08:07.620
is also in turmoil.

08:09.940 --> 08:11.180
My offer still stands.

08:12.300 --> 08:13.590
Will you state your wish?

08:19.790 --> 08:21.620
I promised to show you a good show.

08:22.350 --> 08:23.350
So, I won't have you

08:23.350 --> 08:24.300
lift a finger.

08:31.990 --> 08:33.260
No shackles in this world

08:33.260 --> 08:34.260
can ever hold me.

08:35.140 --> 08:36.740
I think they'll regret

08:37.190 --> 08:38.310
not having pinned

08:38.310 --> 08:39.310
your shoulder blades.

08:40.710 --> 08:41.660
Night is falling.

08:42.430 --> 08:43.590
It's time to end this show.

08:46.780 --> 08:48.260
Well, as a front-row spectator,

08:48.830 --> 08:50.110
I'll just wait and see.

09:18.660 --> 09:24.070
- Bravo!
- Nice!

09:25.230 --> 09:26.070
Now,

09:26.500 --> 09:29.070
Tabai's commander has been taken alive.

09:29.900 --> 09:30.740
Tomorrow,

09:31.110 --> 09:32.990
we'll seize Shuozhou!

09:34.190 --> 09:38.140
Cangshen, grant us victory
and safe return.

09:38.780 --> 09:40.710
Victory and safe return!

09:41.540 --> 09:43.500
Come on. Drink.

09:44.470 --> 09:46.660
Let's drink.

10:28.110 --> 10:28.950
Sneak attack!

10:29.140 --> 10:30.580
We're under attack!

10:30.580 --> 10:31.420
Sneak attack!

10:31.420 --> 10:33.070
We're under attack!

10:41.830 --> 10:42.670
What's going on?

10:43.660 --> 10:44.500
Here.

10:52.840 --> 10:53.710
He's here.

10:53.710 --> 10:54.560
The Liang intruder!

10:54.560 --> 10:55.420
Catch him!

10:58.110 --> 10:58.990
Take him alive.

10:59.230 --> 11:00.190
And you'll be rewarded.

11:00.190 --> 11:01.030
Yes!

11:08.310 --> 11:09.350
- Where?
- Where's he?

11:10.230 --> 11:11.070
Where's the intruder?

11:12.020 --> 11:12.900
South!

11:14.430 --> 11:15.270
Where's the intruder?

11:15.800 --> 11:16.660
The Liang intruder.

11:16.660 --> 11:17.710
He's to the south.

11:18.110 --> 11:19.590
- South.
- He's to the south.

11:20.470 --> 11:21.430
He's to the south.

11:23.750 --> 11:24.730
Catch him!

11:26.070 --> 11:27.380
He's to the east!

11:27.740 --> 11:29.110
He's to the east!

11:29.110 --> 11:30.020
- East.
- East.

11:38.990 --> 11:40.140
Search every corner!

11:40.620 --> 11:42.260
You must find that intruder!

11:42.260 --> 11:43.100
Yes.

11:46.710 --> 11:47.860
- No.
- He's not here.

11:48.950 --> 11:50.380
What's he looking for?

11:50.660 --> 11:51.500
Go look over there!

11:52.070 --> 11:52.910
Yes.

12:16.020 --> 12:16.950
Not in the east.

12:17.260 --> 12:18.500
Not in the south, either.

12:18.710 --> 12:19.620
Go search the north.

12:19.990 --> 12:20.830
Yes.

12:49.540 --> 12:51.660
The horse bolted!

13:00.310 --> 13:01.150
The horse bolted!

13:10.590 --> 13:11.430
Get out of the way!

13:17.540 --> 13:19.380
Fire! Fire!

13:19.710 --> 13:21.900
Put out the fire! Go get water!

13:23.260 --> 13:24.310
- Hurry.
- Fire! Fire!

13:24.310 --> 13:25.380
Put out the fire!

13:25.380 --> 13:26.230
Go get some water!

13:26.230 --> 13:28.660
The tents are on fire. Put it out.

13:30.430 --> 13:31.710
Oh no. The wind is picking up.

13:31.710 --> 13:32.660
It's spreading too fast.

13:32.660 --> 13:33.500
It's too late.

13:34.470 --> 13:36.190
The fire is growing!

13:36.190 --> 13:37.660
Go put it out!

13:42.500 --> 13:43.340
Miss He,

13:44.950 --> 13:45.900
when will the east wind come?

13:46.430 --> 13:47.270
In three days.

13:48.310 --> 13:49.830
That's why he asked me about the wind.

13:54.830 --> 13:56.020
Oh, Foxy.

14:04.260 --> 14:05.260
Get out of the way.

14:21.660 --> 14:23.860
Fire! Put it out!

14:24.020 --> 14:25.740
Get some water! Put it out!

14:27.190 --> 14:28.260
Go get water!

14:33.500 --> 14:34.830
Water.

14:36.110 --> 14:36.950
Give it to me.

15:15.430 --> 15:16.270
Hurry.

15:19.540 --> 15:20.380
General,

15:20.860 --> 15:21.830
our armory is on fire.

15:22.310 --> 15:23.190
The intruder set it.

15:24.660 --> 15:25.540
Darn it!

16:01.990 --> 16:02.830
General,

16:03.070 --> 16:04.310
the Liang man burned our armory.

16:04.590 --> 16:05.660
We haven't found him yet.

16:07.710 --> 16:08.550
General.

16:12.110 --> 16:12.950
General.

16:24.620 --> 16:25.860
Kill him!

16:26.140 --> 16:27.350
Kill!

16:27.860 --> 16:28.830
Put out the fire.

16:28.830 --> 16:29.830
Put it out. Come on.

16:30.860 --> 16:31.700
Water.

16:32.110 --> 16:33.500
Get us some water!

16:33.500 --> 16:34.350
Go put out the fire.

17:50.500 --> 17:51.950
You really didn't see anything?

17:52.540 --> 17:53.380
I saw something.

17:53.780 --> 17:54.630
I saw him enter

17:54.630 --> 17:55.780
the third tent on the left.

17:56.470 --> 17:57.390
However,

17:57.390 --> 17:58.580
he wasn't holding a letter,

17:59.190 --> 18:00.300
but a few goldfish.

18:03.100 --> 18:04.230
Oh, I see.

18:06.230 --> 18:07.780
Arrogant young man.

18:34.230 --> 18:35.070
Duan Xu,

18:36.470 --> 18:37.670
who on earth are you?

18:38.190 --> 18:39.710
Someone from the All-Knowing

18:41.100 --> 18:42.100
can fight a hundred alone

18:42.630 --> 18:44.820
and slay the enemy general
in the heart of their army.

18:45.340 --> 18:46.630
What's so strange about that?

18:47.300 --> 18:48.300
Fifteen,

18:49.100 --> 18:50.230
you got the wrong man.

18:50.870 --> 18:52.470
Han Lingqiu isn't Seventeen.

18:53.230 --> 18:54.340
He should have been dead.

18:54.950 --> 18:56.020
Because he lost to me

18:56.020 --> 18:56.910
in the Trial.

18:58.630 --> 18:59.470
I am

19:03.820 --> 19:05.230
the real Seventeen.

19:17.060 --> 19:17.990
No more waiting.

19:18.390 --> 19:19.950
Otherwise, he will die.

19:19.950 --> 19:20.790
Hey, rally the army.

19:21.020 --> 19:21.860
But...

19:22.710 --> 19:23.550
Look.

19:23.710 --> 19:24.550
It's Xu's signal.

19:25.670 --> 19:26.510
Commandant Wu.

19:26.740 --> 19:27.820
Repel the enemies out there

19:28.260 --> 19:29.740
to at least 50 li further away.

19:29.740 --> 19:30.580
- Yes.
- Captain Meng.

19:31.020 --> 19:32.260
We'll flank the Chong camp

19:32.390 --> 19:33.430
and catch them off guard.

19:33.870 --> 19:34.710
Captain Han,

19:34.710 --> 19:35.630
stay for city defense.

19:38.230 --> 19:39.540
(Oh, I see.)

19:40.430 --> 19:41.540
I graduated at the age of 18

19:42.820 --> 19:44.300
and followed Mentor to meet seniors.

19:45.150 --> 19:46.300
I had just won the Trial,

19:46.300 --> 19:47.230
injured all over.

19:47.630 --> 19:49.540
I almost stumbled
when serving tea to Mentor.

19:50.300 --> 19:51.540
You steadied me.

19:56.190 --> 19:57.820
That was the only time we had ever met.

19:59.020 --> 20:00.190
Am I right,

20:00.950 --> 20:01.790
my senior?

20:02.630 --> 20:04.390
I've always wanted to challenge you.

20:19.820 --> 20:20.780
You deserve punishment

20:21.300 --> 20:22.340
for betraying our mentor!

20:48.950 --> 20:50.470
I've never betrayed anyone.

20:52.950 --> 20:54.780
Because I've never believed in them.

20:57.430 --> 20:58.780
Not even for one single moment.

22:19.100 --> 22:20.630
How ironic.

22:21.710 --> 22:23.100
Someone like you

22:24.060 --> 22:26.540
who abandons his beliefs should die!

22:39.950 --> 22:40.910
Senior,

22:42.910 --> 22:44.710
you wavered in the end.

22:46.470 --> 22:47.710
Otherwise,

22:50.020 --> 22:52.470
how could you make
such a stupid mistake?

25:00.430 --> 25:01.300
Wake up.

25:02.470 --> 25:03.500
You're frantic.

25:41.910 --> 25:43.710
My final mission

25:45.990 --> 25:47.580
was to kill a family of three.

25:59.340 --> 26:00.540
The baby was so young

26:03.950 --> 26:05.150
that I didn't want to kill it.

26:07.190 --> 26:08.340
Mentor found out.

26:10.060 --> 26:11.580
I stabbed out his eyes.

26:13.150 --> 26:13.990
Then, I ran away.

26:19.670 --> 26:20.580
I found a good family

26:20.580 --> 26:21.630
for that baby.

26:23.430 --> 26:24.270
And I...

26:25.870 --> 26:27.430
I then drifted aimlessly

26:30.020 --> 26:31.100
like a rootless duckweed.

26:37.300 --> 26:44.240
♪Cross your legs for three years♪

26:44.260 --> 26:45.260
Kill!

26:46.200 --> 26:48.430
Let's charge in and get the General.

26:49.200 --> 26:52.920
♪Tether horse and ape♪

26:53.160 --> 26:55.910
♪Mind still as water♪

26:55.910 --> 26:56.750
General!

26:57.340 --> 26:58.190
General!

26:58.910 --> 26:59.910
Where's the General?

27:00.300 --> 27:01.260
Find him!

27:01.260 --> 27:02.300
- Yes.
- Yes.

27:05.190 --> 27:06.030
General.

27:09.710 --> 27:10.550
General!

27:10.780 --> 27:11.710
General!

27:12.820 --> 27:13.990
General!

27:14.710 --> 27:15.990
- General.
- General.

27:23.500 --> 27:24.340
Did you tell Meng Wan

27:24.340 --> 27:25.390
to come get you?

27:27.100 --> 27:28.190
I told her.

27:29.740 --> 27:31.150
Not to get me,

27:31.870 --> 27:32.950
but to raid the camp.

27:44.500 --> 27:45.710
There's still a long way to go.

27:46.020 --> 27:47.020
We have to keep going.

27:47.990 --> 27:48.830
Yeah.

27:50.100 --> 27:51.870
There's still such a long road ahead.

27:53.950 --> 27:54.950
But I'm...

27:57.150 --> 27:58.230
I'm exhausted.

28:00.630 --> 28:01.630
Someone who lives

28:01.630 --> 28:02.950
a life of torment

28:03.580 --> 28:04.910
finally gets tired.

28:08.950 --> 28:10.710
The deal we talked about...

28:13.340 --> 28:14.580
Could we do it now?

28:26.100 --> 28:26.940
Never mind.

28:29.300 --> 28:30.710
Forget this deal.

28:34.320 --> 28:35.180
Unless you go back

28:35.200 --> 28:36.710
to Shuozhou and see a doctor,

28:37.710 --> 28:38.870
you will die here.

28:46.740 --> 28:48.150
You want to make a deal with me.

28:50.060 --> 28:51.020
You want my five senses

28:53.300 --> 28:54.580
and promise to return them.

28:55.540 --> 28:57.020
Because you've never experienced

28:57.020 --> 28:57.990
the five senses.

29:01.390 --> 29:02.910
Once you experience colors, flavors,

29:04.230 --> 29:05.390
and temperature changes,

29:06.340 --> 29:08.020
will you still wish to lose them?

29:09.300 --> 29:10.670
Is there going to be a day

29:11.990 --> 29:13.540
when you take away all my senses,

29:16.870 --> 29:17.710
keep me alive

29:17.710 --> 29:18.740
at the brink of death,

29:20.190 --> 29:21.670
and turn me into a living corpse?

29:25.780 --> 29:26.910
Even so,

29:27.710 --> 29:29.060
will you still withstand my spell?

29:39.710 --> 29:40.780
Give me your hand.

29:42.100 --> 29:43.190
Give me your hand

29:45.630 --> 29:46.540
and I'll do it.

29:50.990 --> 29:51.830
Seventeen.

29:52.340 --> 29:53.470
Call me Duan Xu.

29:56.430 --> 29:57.270
Duan Xu,

29:57.580 --> 29:58.820
are you still conscious?

29:59.580 --> 30:00.580
Perfectly conscious.

30:03.100 --> 30:04.260
Isn't this fun?

30:05.260 --> 30:07.340
I wager that when that day comes,

30:10.470 --> 30:11.430
you won't wish to do it.

30:26.230 --> 30:27.070
Deal.

30:51.300 --> 30:52.500
Witnessed by the Pearl,

30:53.230 --> 30:54.300
and bonded by blood,

30:55.540 --> 30:56.380
we make this vow.

31:24.190 --> 31:25.150
The stars blaze.

31:26.230 --> 31:27.260
The Fire Star decrees.

31:30.580 --> 31:31.740
- Your senses
- My senses

31:32.630 --> 31:33.870
- are mine.
- are yours.

31:35.260 --> 31:36.580
Bound in heart,

31:37.990 --> 31:39.470
pledged in soul.

31:47.840 --> 31:53.170
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

31:53.500 --> 31:57.750
♪Light encountered shadow♪

31:59.110 --> 32:04.480
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

32:04.780 --> 32:09.380
♪The unbreakable fate♪

32:10.470 --> 32:12.310
♪Suddenly cracked♪

32:14.920 --> 32:18.080
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

32:18.080 --> 32:20.610
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

32:20.610 --> 32:26.130
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

32:26.130 --> 32:29.370
♪Following fate's guidance♪

32:29.370 --> 32:34.230
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

32:34.570 --> 32:38.040
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

32:46.340 --> 32:48.990
Kill!

32:55.780 --> 32:57.660
(Liang)

33:13.340 --> 33:14.230
What's wrong?

33:19.100 --> 33:20.340
Is something wrong with me?

33:21.230 --> 33:22.230
Does a killing frenzy

33:22.820 --> 33:23.910
mean something wrong?

33:25.150 --> 33:27.230
Before Fifteen died, he said,

33:28.190 --> 33:29.150
"You're also a monster.

33:29.950 --> 33:31.150
You won't get away."

33:31.990 --> 33:33.390
Sometimes I don't know

33:33.540 --> 33:34.390
whether I'm a normal man

33:34.390 --> 33:35.910
pretending to be mad

33:38.500 --> 33:40.150
or a madman pretending to be normal.

33:41.230 --> 33:42.190
Don't be ridiculous

33:42.190 --> 33:43.500
when you're leaning

33:44.580 --> 33:45.710
on the most abnormal person.

33:48.020 --> 33:49.190
That makes sense.

33:52.300 --> 33:53.500
Don't push it.

33:53.820 --> 33:54.740
Let me go.

33:54.740 --> 33:56.230
You want to know who I am, don't you?

34:03.020 --> 34:04.150
I'm Duan Xu.

34:05.870 --> 34:07.630
My grandfather was a famous scholar.

34:09.830 --> 34:10.790
When I was born,

34:11.830 --> 34:13.580
he was watching a play
by Chunsheng Troupe.

34:15.430 --> 34:16.750
Inspired by the lines,

34:16.750 --> 34:17.590
he gave me this name,

34:18.140 --> 34:19.310
which means "military honor".

34:23.950 --> 34:25.020
When I was twelve,

34:25.830 --> 34:27.270
I was abducted by Chong soldiers.

34:28.660 --> 34:30.500
They threatened my father

34:31.310 --> 34:32.950
to hand over intelligence.

34:34.540 --> 34:36.060
My father not only refused,

34:37.270 --> 34:38.350
but also told them,

34:39.870 --> 34:40.950
"You've got the wrong boy.

34:42.270 --> 34:43.220
This isn't Duan Xu,

34:43.220 --> 34:44.660
my third son.

34:46.060 --> 34:47.220
My real son

34:48.350 --> 34:49.580
has been sent to Daizhou

34:51.390 --> 34:52.390
for his grandmother."

34:54.500 --> 34:55.540
The boy who was sent

34:55.540 --> 34:56.380
to Daizhou

34:57.750 --> 34:58.950
was actually an impostor.

34:58.950 --> 35:00.140
Father, help me!

35:00.140 --> 35:01.220
I prayed countless times

35:01.220 --> 35:02.060
Father would save me.

35:02.060 --> 35:02.910
- Father!
- I won't.

35:03.390 --> 35:04.430
Climb out yourself.

35:04.990 --> 35:05.870
But he never came.

35:06.870 --> 35:08.310
The kidnappers were misled.

35:08.910 --> 35:10.100
I seized the chance to escape

35:10.870 --> 35:11.910
and ended up homeless.

35:13.140 --> 35:13.980
Later,

35:14.350 --> 35:15.790
I was chosen by my mentor,

35:15.790 --> 35:16.830
Chief of the All-Knowing,

35:18.020 --> 35:19.500
who was recruiting disciples.

35:20.430 --> 35:21.500
I joined the All-Knowing.

35:26.790 --> 35:27.830
I am Duan Xu,

35:28.870 --> 35:29.750
Duan Shunxi.

35:31.060 --> 35:32.470
I've never lied to you.

35:34.540 --> 35:35.540
See?

35:37.500 --> 35:39.270
I escaped safely again.

36:08.990 --> 36:09.990
Your Grace,

36:12.990 --> 36:14.620
what is your name?

36:15.650 --> 36:18.850
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

36:18.870 --> 36:19.710
He Simu.

36:21.060 --> 36:22.220
H-E, He.

36:22.870 --> 36:24.140
S-I, Si. M-U, Mu.

36:27.390 --> 36:30.110
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

36:30.320 --> 36:33.510
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

36:33.540 --> 36:35.110
He Simu.

36:35.110 --> 36:37.570
♪If I could live a simple life♪

36:37.590 --> 36:38.910
Happy new year.

36:38.910 --> 36:40.970
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

36:40.980 --> 36:43.430
May you always be safe.

36:46.090 --> 36:49.560
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

36:49.790 --> 36:53.400
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

36:53.790 --> 36:57.440
♪Let me wander through♪

36:58.310 --> 36:59.150
Foxy,

37:00.950 --> 37:02.390
may you survive every crisis.

37:05.830 --> 37:06.910
May you live a long life.

37:09.160 --> 37:11.970
♪Moments may last♪

37:12.140 --> 37:18.990
♪Love and hate will fade away♪

37:21.801 --> 37:27.131
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

37:27.461 --> 37:31.711
♪Light encountered shadow♪

37:33.071 --> 37:38.441
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

37:38.741 --> 37:43.341
♪The unbreakable fate♪

37:44.431 --> 37:46.271
♪Suddenly cracked♪

37:58.481 --> 38:03.921
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

38:04.101 --> 38:08.431
♪Light encountered shadow♪

38:09.801 --> 38:15.191
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:15.421 --> 38:19.361
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:21.131 --> 38:23.021
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:25.681 --> 38:28.841
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

38:28.841 --> 38:31.371
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

38:31.371 --> 38:36.891
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

38:36.891 --> 38:40.131
♪Following fate's guidance♪

38:40.131 --> 38:44.991
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

38:45.331 --> 38:48.351
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

38:48.351 --> 38:51.171
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

38:51.431 --> 38:53.961
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

38:53.961 --> 38:59.381
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

38:59.551 --> 39:02.621
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

39:02.781 --> 39:07.681
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

39:07.891 --> 39:11.361
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
